      "content": "i know there are resources. i know people want to help. it’s just that nothing helps. it feels like i’m just stuck in this loop of hurting. like the pain is the only thing that's actually real anymore. everything else is just empty. how am i supposed to just \"reach out\" and keep living like this?",
